<span id="Description"></span>
==Описание==

The '''View Measure Clear All''' command clears the active [[3D_view|3D view]]'s [[Part_Workbench|Part]] measurements.

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Применение==

# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|View → Visibility → [[Image:View_Measure_Clear_All.svg|16px]] Clear measurement}} option from the menu.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Measure → [[Image:View_Measure_Clear_All.svg|16px]] Clear measurement}} option from the 3D view context menu.

<span id="Notes"></span>
==Примечания==

* Эта команда идентична команде [[Part_Measure_Clear_All/ru|Part Measure Clear All]].


